01:32:05,330 --> 01:32:06,540
Wacht.

1
01:32:06,620 --> 01:32:10,370
M'n liefje. Wacht.

1
01:32:10,460 --> 01:32:12,460
Gollem. Gollem.

1
01:32:17,510 --> 01:32:19,300
Vlug.

1
01:32:21,430 --> 01:32:22,720
Daglicht. Kom op.

1
